name: 2014 Calendar
description:
Happy New Year!
Look forward to the days ahead as you glance fondly at this 12 month calendar.
– size 8” x 10”
– blank on back
– crisp digital printing on bright white 110# cover
– choose from 2 colors: black or rich orchid
– fits standard 8” x 10” frame

name: Bash! Digital File
description:
And just like that, it's a party!
Supplies and spirits, check! Now, make your own invitation prints from the provided digital file and you're ready to gather your guests for an affair to remember.
– customization instructions listed below – Letter size (8 1/2” x 11” flat) PDF document – Must be trimmed to finished invitation size (5" x 7") – choose from 6 colors (see swatch image): poppy, eggplant, emerald, black, magenta or navy
Please provide the following information at checkout in the “Instructions to Merchant” section: LINE 1: Name and occasion to celebrate LINE 2: Day, date and time of occasion LINE 3: Food and/or activities at the occasion LINE 4: Location(s) and/or address of occasion LINE 5: Host of and RSVP to occasion
Within one business day, we’ll email you a PDF proof of the invitation. Please review all content carefully and approve the proof within 24 hours. Once we receive your final approval, we'll email you a completed digital file in printable PDF format within one business day.
NOTE: Enter code "DIGITAL" at checkout to waive shipping costs.

name: Seasonal Postcards
description:
A little message goes a long way.
Whether you're basking in the sun poolside or nestled in a blanket fireside, spread that warmth to dear friends near and far with this simple postcard.
– size 4 1/8” x 5 13/16” – space for message and address on back – Printed on crisp white 130# cover – Glossy laminate finish on image side, unlaminated satin finish on reverse – Includes one postcard in each design (Merry Christmas scene, Merry Christmas lights, Seasons Greetings in holly red and Seasons Greetings in olive) for a total of 4 postcards – packaged in clear protective sleeve

name: Flourish Notecard
description:
Seal it with a KISS and Keep It Simple and Sincere. These delicate flourishes frame the work of art that is your words.
– A2 size (5 1/2” x 4 1/4” flat) – blank on back – offset printing in beautiful metallic gold on white 130# cover – matching white Euro flap envelope

name: Congrats Notecard
description:
Seal it with a KISS and Keep It Simple and Sincere. Yea! Nice job! Flattery (with this card) will get you everywhere.
– A2 size (5 1/2” x 4 1/4” flat) – blank on back – offset printing in beautiful metallic gold on white 130# cover – matching white Euro flap envelope

name: Party Coasters
description:
Drinks are on us.
These party coasters are the perfect cocktail compliment for any occasion.
– size 4” round – blank on back – light letterpress impression in metallic gold on extra thick off-white pulp board

name: The Metallic Collection
description:
From the Metallic Collection Correspondence worth its weight in gold.
– A2 size card (5 1/2” x 4 1/4” folded) – blank inside – offset printing in beautiful metallic gold on white 100# cover – matching white Euro flap envelope – choose from Sunburst, Stripes, Branches or Variety (four cards in each of the three designs) – available as boxed sets of 12

name: The Pitter Pattern Collection
description:
From the Pitter Pattern Collection Classic menswear-inspired stationery with a refined and relaxed style is definitely noteworthy.
– 4 bar size card (4 7/8” x 3 1/2” folded) – blank inside – rich black foil stamped pattern on white 100# cover – matching white Euro flap envelope – choose from Houndstooth, Herringbone, Chevron or Variety (two cards in each of the three patterns) – available as boxed sets of 6

Foil stamping leaves a light surface impression with a subtle sheen.

name: The Pitter Collection
description:
From the Pitter Collection Write. Send. Repeat. Do you see a pattern forming here?
– 4 bar size card (3 1/2” x 4 7/8” folded) – blank inside – offset printing in harvest on white 100# cover – natural Kraft Euro flap envelope (30% PCW) – choose from Houndstooth, Herringbone, Chevron or Variety (two cards in each of the three designs) – available as boxed sets of 6
Harvest is a golden yellow color with an undertone of olive green.

name: Mr. & Mrs. Mini Cards
description:
"I do" want to include this with a gift.
This enclosure card may be small in size, but it's big on sentiment. Oh, and the happy couple is sure to appreciate the gift that comes with it, too.
– flat size 2.5” x 3.5” – blank on back – offset printing in black on white 130# cover – matching white envelope

name: Holiday Gift Tags
description:
Tag yourself a merry little Christmas.
Make the Yule-tide and your packages happy and bright.
– size 2 3/4” x 1” – blank on back – available in three design sets: Snowfall (trees, snow and bark) or Festive (basket, stars and pinecone) or Wonderland (branches, sunburst and stripes) – each set includes three tags in each of three designs in each of three colors (maroon, olive and bright green) for a total of nine tags – printed on crisp white 130# cover – 10” strand of waxed linen thread included with each tag

name: Celebration Gift Tags
description:
Tag, you're it.
Present your present with a sophisticated finishing touch.
– size 2 3/4” x 1” – blank on back – available in two design sets: Festive (basket, stars and pinecone) or Wonderland (branches, sunburst and stripes) – each set includes three tags in each of three designs in each of three colors (gold, silver and navy) for a total of nine tags – printed on crisp white 130# cover – 10” strand of waxed linen thread included with each tag

name: Many Thanks Notecard
description:
Seal it with a KISS and Keep It Simple and Sincere. When one “thank you” just isn’t enough, many thanks should do the trick.
– A2 size (5 1/2” x 4 1/4” flat) – blank on back – offset printing in choice of metallic gold or black on white 130# cover – matching white Euro flap envelope

name: Hello Notecard
description:
Seal it with a KISS and Keep It Simple and Sincere. Say hello to the perfect card for saying a simple hello.
– A2 size (5 1/2” x 4 1/4” flat) – blank on back – offset printing in black on white 130# cover – matching white Euro flap envelope

name: K.I.T. Notecard
description:
Seal it with a KISS and Keep It Simple and Sincere. Keep in touch with all of the high school friends you wrote that promise to in their yearbooks.
– A2 size (5 1/2” x 4 1/4” flat) – blank on back – offset printing in black on white 130# cover – matching white Euro flap envelope

name: Enjoy Notecard
description:
Seal it with a KISS and Keep It Simple and Sincere. Enjoy giving this card as much as the gift that accompanies it.
– A2 size (5 1/2” x 4 1/4” flat) – blank on back – offset printing in black on white 130# cover – matching white Euro flap envelope

name: Happy Couple Notecards
description:
It's wedding season! Give the perfect gift with personalized Happy Couple stationery. Send us a message for complete information. With liberty and marriage for all. Mr. & Mr. Notecard: With this card, stand by your man and show the world you love him.
Mr. & Mrs. Notecard: Pronounce the happy couple as husband and wife all over again with this timeless card.
Mrs. & Mrs. Notecard: Happy wife, happy life. This card honors the commitment of two lovely ladies.
– A2 size (5 1/2” x 4 1/4” flat) – blank on back – offset printing in black on white 130# cover – matching white Euro flap envelope
